    h1 RSS to ActivityPub Converter
    p.account code by <a href="https://friend.camp/@darius">Darius Kazemi</a>, <a href="https://jabberwocky.moe/@alice">umonaca</a>, and adapted for easy deployment by <a href="https://huey.xyz">Huey</a>
    p This is a service to convert any RSS feed into an account that Mastodon, Pleroma, Misskey (or any other ActivityPub social network) can subscribe to. <a href="https://github.com/hueyy/rss-to-activitypub">Source code here</a>.
    p <a href="/convert/">Click here to start!</a>
    p Only users of <a href="https://#{OAUTH.domain}">#{OAUTH.domain_human}</a> can create feeds, but anyone can subscribe if they know the account info.
    p <a href="https://#{OAUTH.domain}#{OAUTH.authorize_path}?scope=read:accounts&response_type=code&redirect_uri=#{OAUTH.redirect_uri}&client_id=#{OAUTH.client_id}">Click here to log in!</a>
